  "keyFeatures": [
    "47 modern JavaFX components with consistent styling",
    "Tailwind CSS-inspired design system with semantic color tokens",
    "Built-in dark mode support with CSS variables",
    "Advanced SQL editor with syntax highlighting and validation",
    "Comprehensive form controls (inputs, selects, checkboxes, switches)",
    "Rich data display components (tables, lists, cards, avatars)",
    "Navigation components (sidebar, breadcrumbs, pagination, tabs)",
    "Feedback components (alerts, toasts, modals, progress indicators)",
    "Design canvas for drag-and-drop field composition",
    "Icon integration with Ikonli (Feather and Material Design packs)",
    "Easy theme initialization with single method call",
    "Export functionality for data (Excel, CSV)"
  ],
